name: LOTOBoatingForecast
0: ”Alexa, ask LOTO Boating if we should boat Saturday?”
skdetail:

Invocation Name: loto boating
des:
An example use case would, ask LOTO Boating if we should boat Saturday? 
It will then retrieve the LOTO forecast for Saturday and give you the details of the forecast and an opinion of whether you should be boating.
